page.title: 12Weekend
page.content: My name is Zoie I am eleven.On sunday morning I woke up at 9.55,then I dressed and went downstairs.I had cornflakes for my breakfast ,then me and my family went to pick up my friend to go swimming.When we got back we had our lunch we had spaghetti on toast.Afterwards we went outside ,after awhile we went for a walk in the fields.When we came back me and my friend went in for our tea we had a roast.At 8.00 we took my friend home.I done my homework when I got home,afterwards I watched t.v. .At 9.45 i had my supper, at 10.10 I went to bed.
